04e05849-ea28-458a-8b78-ac971c5d1d06.content:
**cd**: changes current directory, takes one argument\
**ls**: lists everything in current directory, can take multiple arguments to check permissions

e074d7ca-adb7-44c2-83c8-ec9366f8d986.title: Data
e074d7ca-adb7-44c2-83c8-ec9366f8d986.content:
list => list of elements (sometimes called slice or table)\
array => slices/list that have a restricted amount of elements determined in the variable assignment\
dictionary/hash => key-value data structure\
tuple => immutable list
